{"tid":2392179,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"GME輸晒嘅希望幫到大家","createTime":"2021-02-02T15:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T03:31:55.000Z","uid":76745,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8db801cac7d904633cae8501611d5a2a13ffad9f","tid":2392179,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.oro.gov.hk/cht/publications/bankguide.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oro.gov.hk%2Fcht%2Fpublications%2Fbankguide.htm&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrW5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=04768fe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oro.gov.hk/cht/publications/bankguide.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n債務人呈請<br />\n<br />\n2.2 債務人提交破產呈請的程序是：<br />\n  <br />\n(a) 填妥《破產(表格)規則》表格3&ldquo;債務人破產呈請書&rdquo;和《破產(表格)規則》表格28C&ldquo;資產負債狀況說明書（債務人的呈請）&rdquo;。&ldquo;債務人破產呈請程序簡介&rdquo;內已包括上述各份表格，市民可以透過本署互聯網免費下載：<br />\n「網址：<a href=\"http://www.oro.gov.hk/cht/publications/debtor.htm」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oro.gov.hk%2Fcht%2Fpublications%2Fdebtor.htm%E3%80%8D&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrW5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=c516a7f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.oro.gov.hk/cht/publications/debtor.htm」</a><br />\n市民亦可以用以下方法獲取該簡介，費用為每本18元 :-<br />\n  <br />\n(i) 致電政府新聞處刊物銷售小組訂購<br />\n電話：2537 1910<br />\n(ii) 進入網上『政府書店』選購各類刊物 (<a href=\"http://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/publication/publication/bookstore.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fgovernment%2Fpublication%2Fpublication%2Fbookstore.htm&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrW5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=02d1a802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/publication/publication/bookstore.htm</a>)<br />\n(iii) 透過政府新聞處的網站(<a href=\"http://www.isd.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.isd.gov.hk&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrW5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=3980d6fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.isd.gov.hk</a>)於網上遞交訂購表格，或將表格傳真至刊物銷售小組<br />\n(傳真：2523 7195)。<br />\n(iv) 以電郵方式訂購「電郵地址：puborder@isd.gov.hk」。<br />\n(v)  在本署購買。<br />\n(b)  向破產管理署署長繳存一筆8,000元的款項, 以供支付破產管理署署長(或受託人)將會招致的各項費用及開支；<br />\n(c) 就呈請找得見證並就資產負債狀況說明書宣誓；<br />\n(d) 前往高等法院登記處：<br />\n  <br />\n(i)  繳付法庭費用1,045元；<br />\n(ii)  就呈請取得聆訊的日期；及<br />\n(iii)  提交呈請書和資產負債狀況說明書；及<br />\n(e) 在完成(d)(iii)後，立即向破產管理署署長提交呈請書的蓋印副本和資產負債狀況說明書的副本。"},{"pid":"fa304c0f24d4e3d6d344604a7d64da9b51371103","tid":2392179,"uid":76745,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"推 幾年後又冇事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104cc2f2df47779b731402b4ab6c3504ff1a125e","tid":2392179,"uid":127251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6582eee4ad8b3b339ce285e224f617f0c17fe5eb","tid":2392179,"uid":243691,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"你條仆街攞景定贈慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212dee81b39290a7310103eb6a5baeef8e9f04e7","tid":2392179,"uid":358604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n<br />\n利民會《即時通》：35122626<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"116dd55c2a7241811debc24cb50d3a9cafa0a360","tid":2392179,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6582eee4ad8b3b339ce285e224f617f0c17fe5eb","tid":2392179,"uid":243691,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"cit